<button class="accordion">What is the first step of manual handling?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>The first step in approaching any manual handling task, whether in care or otherwise, is to establish what the risks might be. By moving a person, is there a risk that you might hurt yourself, or that the person could be hurt?</p>
</div>
<button class="accordion">What is the most vulnerable part of the body when manual handling?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>The back is the most vulnerable part of the body when poor technique is used. The lower back is subjected to ten times the weight of the object lifted.</p>
