<button class="accordion">What are the five principles of safe manual handling?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>The 5 Ps of safe manual handling are as follows:</p>
<li> Plan</li>
<li> Position</li>
<li> Pick Up</li>
<li> Proceed</li>
<li> Put down.</li>
</div>
