<button class="accordion">Why is manual handling training important?</button>
<div class="panel">
<p>Manual handling training will help increase employees' awareness of the risks involved with lifting. Further, employees will also recognise that their welfare is top priority, and the course will lead to fewer people taking time off work due to injury.</p>
